'''Desiree Garcia''' (2168 - 2203) was an American actress. She was the daughter of art gallery professional [[Lynn Garcia]], granddaughter of magician [[Odell Garcia]], great-granddaughter of businessman [[Eduardo Garcia]], great-great-granddaughter of baseball player [[Colt Garcia]], and great-great-great-granddaughter of musician [[Donald Garcia]]. 

